==Getting started==
===Talking to Little Mo===
* '''Player:''' Hello, I've not seen you around here before, who are you?
* '''Little Mo:''' Hi! You can call me Mo, I'm a travelling trader and I've just relocated to Lumbridge.
* '''Player:''' Nice to meet you, Mo! So what kind of wares do you trade in?
* '''Little Mo:''' I usually deal in just about anything and everything!
* '''Player:''' Usually? You don't any more?
* '''Little Mo:''' Well, I've recently acquired an interesting artifact{{sic|Uses american spelling instead of british spelling}} in a trade and would like to have it examined by a specialist at the Varrock Museum.
* '''Little Mo:''' Sadly though I can't afford to let my business suffer by going away and the Museum specialist is leaving very soon on an expedition.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I could take it to the Museum for you!}}
** '''Player:''' I could take it to the Museum for you!
** '''Little Mo:''' Thanks for the offer but I'm not letting this artifact out of my sight.
** '''Little Mo:''' Although you still might be able to help, would you be interested in completing some deliveries for me while I head to Varrock?
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|What's in it for me?}}
*** '''Player:''' Sure, I could deliver to the farthest reaches of the world... but what's in it for me?
*** '''Little Mo:''' Well, I'm taking a huge gamble on this artifact being valuable. I'm willing to offer you a share of its final sale price.
*** '''Player:''' What if it's worth nothing? I'll have wasted my time!
*** '''Little Mo:''' Welcome to the world of trading my friend! Are you in or are you out?
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|You've got yourself a deal!}}
**** '''Player:''' You've got yourself a deal! What do you need me to do?
**** '''Little Mo:''' If you search my cart you'll find some packages for delivery. Each package is labelled but in order to protect my customers' privacy they're a little vague.
**** '''Little Mo:''' I don't have time to explain exactly where everyone is so I'm afraid you'll have to do a bit of searching to find them.
**** '''Player:''' Take packages from cart, deliver to the person on the label. Doesn't sound too hard!
**** '''Little Mo:''' It may be harder than you think but I must leave now for Varrock, I will return soon, thanks for your assistance my friend!
**** '''Player:''' Good luck!
**** {{tbox|Mo hurries off towards Varrock.}}
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{topt|No thanks.}}
**** {{tmissing}}
** {{topt|No thanks.}}
*** {{tmissing}}
* {{topt|That's quite a situation, good luck with it.}}
** {{tmissing}}

==Delivering the packages==
===Searching the cart===
* {{tbox|pic=Package detail.png|You find a labelled package ready for delivery.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Inspecting the first package===
* {{tbox|This package is addressed to {{colour|blue|A man near some trees.}}}}
* '''Player:''' Mo wasn't kidding about these being vaguely labelled, I'd better start looking!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Man near Musa Point===
* '''Player:''' Hello, I think I have a delivery for you...
* '''Man:''' Ah finally my eastern crystals! Where is Mo? I've never known him to trust anyone else with his business!
* '''Player:''' He's busy running another errand so I offered to help him with some deliveries.
* '''Man:''' Ah well that is nice of you, thanks for this!
* {{tact|end}}

===Inspecting the second package===
* {{tbox|This package is addressed to {{colour|blue|A guard in a high position.}}}}
* '''Player:''' Ugh... this could be any guard, most don't have ranks!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the Guard upstairs at Port Sarim jail===
* '''Player:''' Hello?
* '''Guard:''' What? Who goes there? What do you want?
* '''Player:''' I have a delivery for you from Little Mo.
* '''Guard:''' Oh yes my Herblore supplies! Thanks!
* {{tact|end}}

===Inspecting the third package===
* {{tbox|This package is addressed to {{colour|blue|A wanderer of the Wilderness.}}}}
* '''Player:''' Great, the wilderness... I'd better be careful!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to William in the Wilderness===
* '''Player:''' Hi, expecting a delivery from Little Mo?
* '''William:''' Indeed I am, what do you know about it?
* '''Player:''' I have it here for you, Mo has been busy so I'm helping him out.
* '''William:''' Brilliant! I've been expecting these supplies for weeks. Thanks!
* {{tact|end}}

==Finishing up==
===Talking to Little Mo after delivering all packages===
* '''Player:''' Welcome back Mo, you've been gone a while. What happened at the museum?
* '''Little Mo:''' My friend, I have been on a most strange adventure!
* '''Player:''' Adventure? I thought you were just heading to Varrock Museum?
* '''Little Mo:''' Well it's quite a long story, are you sure you want to hear it now?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Yes please tell me the story now.}}
** '''Player:''' Yes, please tell me the story now.
** '''Little Mo:''' Well, everything was going to plan at the museum, the specialist examined the artifact and explained that it was actually part of an ancient and powerful, much larger stone.
** '''Player:''' Incredible! So it's valuable then?
** '''Little Mo:''' Well that's what I thought but as I left the museum I was approached by a hooded man who tried to take it from me!
** '''Little Mo:''' Now I'm not stupid and have had people try and steal from me before... but this guy was different and had some kind of special powers I simply couldn't fight.
** '''Little Mo:''' I woke up in a daze, without the artifact, not entirely sure what had happened.
** '''Player:''' So the artifact is gone... are you okay?
** '''Little Mo:''' I am my friend but this is just the start of the story.
** '''Little Mo:''' A man from the Legends' Guild saw what happened and helped me up, he spoke of some kind of temple and offered to help me retrieve the artifact.
** '''Little Mo:''' Naturally I accepted though I was unsure of his motives at first.
** '''Little Mo:''' We travelled to the jungle and a battlefield and encountered many dangers before meeting some knights of Falador.
** '''Player:''' Wow! Did you manage to recover the artifact?
** '''Little Mo:''' If you'll allow me to continue my friend...
** '''Little Mo:''' I was with the Knights for quite some time and they waffled on a lot but I heard them mention Lumbridge caves a few times.
** '''Little Mo:''' Growing impatient and worrying about my business here I decided to leave and explore the caves on my way back.
** '''Player:''' So what did you find?
** '''Little Mo:''' Deep within the cave I encountered the hooded man with a giant boulder, so I tried to confront him.
** '''Little Mo:''' Before I could even get close I was attacked by some fiery demonic beings and he was able to get away.
** '''Player:''' Sorry to hear you came back empty handed, Mo...
** '''Little Mo:''' Well I did manage to defeat the demons and got these red spiky things...
** {{tbox|pic=Diango's claws detail.png|Mo shows you what he found deep within the Lumbridge Caves.}}
** '''Little Mo:''' I don't know what they are but would you like them? Consider it a thank you for protecting my business.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Sure, they might do something cool.}}
*** '''Player:''' Sure, they might do something cool.
*** {{tbox|pic=Diango's claws detail.png|Mo gives you the item he found beneath Lumbridge.}}
*** '''Player:''' Thanks Mo, so what's next for you?
*** '''Little Mo:''' I'll stick to trading from my cart from now on but as for where I end up next, who knows...
*** '''Little Mo:''' It was a pleasure to meet you my friend, Goodbye!
*** {{tbox|Little Mo picks up his cart and heads off into the distance.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No thanks they look like junk to me.}}
*** {{tmissing}}
* {{topt|I'm a little busy now, I'll come back later.}}
** {{tmissing}}

